# Release notes template

Copy this file to ``RELEASE_NOTES.md`` and fill in the sections that
apply, then commit it together with the ``VERSION`` bump.

The GitHub Actions release workflow (``.github/workflows/release.yml``)
refuses to publish a release if ``RELEASE_NOTES.md`` is missing or
smaller than 64 bytes, so don't leave it empty.

The file contents become the GitHub Release body verbatim -- write it
for end users, not for fellow developers. Engineering changelog
detail belongs in ``ISSUES.md`` (institutional memory) and the git
log (commit messages).

---

## Highlights

- One bullet per user-visible change.

## Install

Same as the previous release -- extract the zip into your GTA IV
install folder. See the bundled ``README.txt`` for the full
walkthrough.

## Requirements

- GTA IV: The Complete Edition v1.2.0.43 (Rockstar Launcher or Steam)
- Ultimate ASI Loader (``dinput8.dll``)
- FusionFix 5.x recommended

